node.text: Y’all are always asking for Charleston recommendations. My favorite places are the ones off the beaten path that still feel authentic. Not many of them left. @humgrocery on Wadmalaw Island is one of them. Tomato pies, fresh Lima beans and the best BBQ sammies! Come check them out!
